<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_61a95bb1-ab4b-4878-91f9-b0349885ac48" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J4D4</sptc><title id="_55283127-09d1-45ae-931a-dbbaca983464">Roof and ceiling construction</title><archive-num>2019: J1.3</archive-num><subclause id="_167ed5d7-6d49-475c-aa8e-490068c9f60b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d24126c7-2492-496f-8549-c6bf9d74d525">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A roof or ceiling must achieve a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1490_25.4.0.xml#_bf26e61b-dbc1-4c09-b8be-ac8d936c0ac9" id="_fbb5d6ca-06c8-46f3-9db4-d299c92c4db8" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Total R-Value</xref> greater than or equal to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_3151ad89-cd8e-46cc-91ca-d47a6d88c01f">for a Class 5, 6, 7, 8 or 9b building or a Class 9a building other than a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1512_27.0.0.xml#_1cef9012-a558-4d8d-a378-daa863164a92" id="_dac886e2-47cb-4c28-9fd6-f3275afc6f2d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">ward area</xref>—<ol><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_80828067-613d-4f70-b144-3b27e2dc569c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zones</xref> 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 — R3.7 for a downward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_8cb05632-8d57-4b03-bc7c-bb95180948c8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 6 — R3.2 for a downward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_2c4f9e49-ac86-4651-a150-ac3388acc6af" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 7 — R3.7 for an upward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_80d3f503-57c8-44d6-8ae5-8865544ed477" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 8 — R4.8 for an upward direction of heat flow.</li></ol></li><li id="_5299fdcc-ce8e-4362-ab5a-23185dbee667">for a Class 3 or 9c building or a Class 9a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1512_27.0.0.xml#_d1b612a5-df98-4406-ba1e-237f837e1061" id="_0860eb48-e4a3-4de8-ae71-c130b3543a04" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">ward area</xref>—<ol><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_4af7d852-5e48-4fa8-bba3-f9e3f8e7472c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1, 3, 4 and 6 — R4.8 for a downward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_98e27f15-fcf3-4308-9adb-c5f62713652f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 2 — R4.4 for a downward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_f5f79748-29ec-496b-ab94-3ed44bce38d7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 5 — R3.7 for a downward direction of heat flow; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_0978a56b-cbd6-4a8b-9cf9-659fbe4731ad" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 7 and 8 — R5.3 in an upward direction of heat flow.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_44ae89c0-58ed-45d4-9423-1acb066b4412" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a75f04a6-c151-43ca-9a7f-c787f7b41592">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>In <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_a7a76039-31ed-4981-91f8-d75f224b952a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 and 7 the upper surface of a roof must have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_43ccccd8-a340-4d79-885d-8a5c1e2b34ee">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/9510_0.4.0.xml#_f5469860-4e39-430c-8ed6-2f36855e45cc" id="_e985beb5-e24f-407f-8d1e-1ff41cebff4b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Total Solar Reflectance</xref> greater than 0.55 and a thermal emittance greater than 0.85; or</li><li id="_cadf55fe-6636-45ac-bdef-11562c28e184">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/9490_0.3.0.xml#_9d98aedb-9334-46be-9e97-5c20584ebdb1" id="_825002eb-06a1-4228-922b-1217d208dff4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Solar Reflectance Index</xref> greater than 61; or</li><li id="_69dceeb6-fd8b-4013-ac03-31877418ab91">a solar absorptance of not more than 0.45 and a thermal emittance of greater than 0.85.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_3d07f08a-e639-43a1-bc99-b295626980be" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_963012a1-fa90-4670-8ab9-a2de893eda7f">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>In <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_0be38ebe-eb20-45aa-a7a8-4348c88218de" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1, 2, 3, 5 and 6 the upper surface of a metal roof, which has outside air intakes, unitary air-conditioning units or air-cooled chillers mounted on it or less than 2 m above it, must have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b0ba79f3-7f82-464c-8b01-8992fb8783f7">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/9510_0.4.0.xml#_f5469860-4e39-430c-8ed6-2f36855e45cc" id="_13f36950-726d-44a7-8360-e863a476250f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Total Solar Reflectance</xref> greater than 0.65 and a thermal emittance greater than 0.85; or</li><li id="_9e70c707-f764-47c9-a7c9-d4d1cc1df0ea">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/9490_0.3.0.xml#_9d98aedb-9334-46be-9e97-5c20584ebdb1" id="_f55ea24f-0475-4984-aa09-81d6bcb8e2ef" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Solar Reflectance Index</xref> greater than 80; or</li><li id="_a7aaa3b6-8324-4482-b8dd-b2cf8e986879">a solar absorptance of not more than 0.35 and a thermal emittance of greater than 0.85.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f08fdca4-8289-47a6-a407-d311eaa41a87" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_15235ea1-67ef-4841-850b-aff9c88e1007">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The requirements of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3382_3.11.0.xml#_73c6664d-a96f-41f2-bc50-f0ae0725dafb" id="_98ad4786-1656-4c5e-92f9-4e0e39d8517d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">(2)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3382_3.11.0.xml#_9dc0635d-1cf2-442d-b76d-0f3254d599b2" id="_6805860d-9c45-488f-81cb-151c574cd54b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">(3)</xref> do not apply to the portion of the upper surface of a roof that is beneath a solar photovoltaic panel or a rooftop garden.</p></subclause></clause>